title.rendered: Alticor Inc Named 2015 Large General Contractor of the Year by Associated Subcontractors Alliance

content.rendered:
On Wednesday, July 22, 2015, Alticor Inc was named the Large General Contractor of the Year by the Associated Subcontractors Alliance (ASA) – San Diego at the 25th Annual Awards & Installation Banquet, held at the Mission Valley Marriott.

The Large General Contractor should exhibit fairness and practice professionalism. Their construction management and project administration efforts are done in a confident and efficient manner. Their ethical standards are always followed, they conduct projects in a safe manner, and their safety standards are adhered to and enforced. Finally, this contractor makes payments in accordance with contract terms. – http://sandiegoasa.org/
